  "description": "P3 (C1+C2 high school 모의고사 passage) viewed by a B1 student — 영어 포기 학생이 본인 수준보다 두 단계 이상 위의 지문을 읽는 시나리오. Range is B1-C1 across all 3 lists. C2 content is excluded. Even so, the target list is large because the passage is dense and almost everything B2/C1 is new for the student. expectedTextFit is too_hard (C2 peak is 3 levels above B1).",
